#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.98"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.98:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.98:0.2"
msgid "10. Kakudhavagga"
msgstr "10. With Kakudha"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: catutthaakuppasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.98:0.3"
msgid "98. Āraññakasutta"
msgstr "98. In the Wilderness"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.98:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu ānāpānassatiṃ "
"bahulīkaronto nacirasseva akuppaṃ paṭivijjhati."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant practicing mindfulness of breathing who has five "
"things will soon penetrate the unshakable."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.98:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu appaṭṭho hoti appakicco subharo susantoso "
"jīvitaparikkhāresu;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has few requirements and duties, and is easily looked "
"after and contented with life’s necessities."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.4"
msgid "appāhāro hoti anodarikattaṃ anuyutto;"
msgstr "They eat little, not devoted to filling their stomach."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.5"
msgid "appamiddho hoti jāgariyaṃ anuyutto;"
msgstr "They are rarely drowsy, and are dedicated to wakefulness."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.6"
msgid "āraññako hoti pantasenāsano;"
msgstr "They live in the wilderness, in remote lodgings."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.7"
msgid "yathāvimuttaṃ cittaṃ paccavekkhati."
msgstr "They review the extent of their mind’s freedom."

msgctxt "an5.98:1.8"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu ānāpānassatiṃ "
"bahulīkaronto nacirasseva akuppaṃ paṭivijjhatī”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant practicing mindfulness of breathing who has these five things "
"will soon penetrate the unshakable.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.98:1.9"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
